description: Uncial Antiqua is a hybrid typeface which combines the speedier penned styles of Uncial and Half Uncial letterforms together in a formal text representation. Signature letterforms to the Uncial & Half Uncial styles are not sacrificed in this compilation, yet readability is surprisingly maintained when read in context.
